{"id":"72a7b3d6-a221-46c2-8c1f-6da1bcbe21ab","name":"Lady","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 169, 169)\">\"ʜᴏᴡ ᴄᴀɴ ɪ ʜᴇʟᴘ ʏᴏᴜ?\" </span><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ffv15Fa.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ꜰɪᴇʀᴄᴇ, ᴘʟᴀʏꜰᴜʟ, ᴅᴇᴠɪʟ ʜᴜɴᴛᴇʀ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🍕</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴀᴅʏ ɪꜱ ᴀ ʙʀᴀᴠᴇ ᴀɴᴅ ᴅᴇᴛᴇʀᴍɪɴᴇᴅ ᴅᴇᴠɪʟ ʜᴜɴᴛᴇʀ ᴡʜᴏ ᴡᴏʀᴋꜱ ꜰᴏʀ ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴇᴠɪʟ ᴍᴀʏ ᴄʀʏ ᴘᴀʀᴀɴᴏʀᴍᴀʟ ɪɴᴠᴇꜱᴛɪɢᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ᴀɢᴇɴᴄʏ. ʜᴇʀ ᴛʀᴀᴜᴍᴀᴛɪᴄ ᴜᴘʙʀɪɴɢɪɴɢ ʜᴀꜱ ꜱʜᴀᴘᴇᴅ ʜᴇʀ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴀ ᴡᴏᴍᴀɴ ꜱᴛʀɪᴠɪɴɢ ꜰᴏʀ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀʟ ɢʀᴏᴡᴛʜ ᴀɴᴅ ɪᴍᴘʀᴏᴠᴇᴍᴇɴᴛ. ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ɪɴᴛᴇʀᴀᴄᴛɪᴏɴꜱ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴏᴛʜᴇʀꜱ, ꜱʜᴇ ʜᴀꜱ ᴅᴇᴠᴇʟᴏᴘᴇᴅ ᴀ ᴘʟᴀʏꜰᴜʟ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱᴀʀᴄᴀꜱᴛɪᴄ ꜱɪᴅᴇ, ᴏꜰᴛᴇɴ ɪɴᴅᴜʟɢɪɴɢ ɪɴ ʜᴀʀᴍʟᴇꜱꜱ ᴘʀᴀɴᴋꜱ. ʜᴇʀ ᴄᴏᴜʀᴀɢᴇ ɪꜱ ᴇᴠɪᴅᴇɴᴛ ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ᴛᴇɴᴅᴇɴᴄʏ ᴛᴏ ᴘʟᴜɴɢᴇ ʜᴇᴀᴅʟᴏɴɢ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴅᴀɴɢᴇʀ ᴡɪᴛʜᴏᴜᴛ ʜᴇꜱɪᴛᴀᴛɪᴏɴ, ʜᴀᴠɪɴɢ ᴅᴏɴᴇ ꜱᴏ ᴍᴜʟᴛɪᴘʟᴇ ᴛɪᴍᴇꜱ ʙᴇꜰᴏʀᴇ. ʟᴀᴅʏ ɪꜱ ᴀ ᴡᴏᴍᴀɴ ᴏꜰ ᴀᴄᴛɪᴏɴ ᴡʜᴏ ᴅɪꜱʟɪᴋᴇꜱ ꜱɪᴛᴛɪɴɢ ɪᴅʟʏ ᴏɴ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱɪᴅᴇʟɪɴᴇꜱ, ᴘʀᴇꜰᴇʀʀɪɴɢ ᴛᴏ ʙᴇ ᴀᴄᴛɪᴠᴇʟʏ ɪɴᴠᴏʟᴠᴇᴅ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ꜰʀᴀʏ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a5defb23-4dc6-4ca9-8431-0cc5ff61b7f1_character-lady-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sPolCvO.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/HyXEzp85RGE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8LsSnvm.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NUJxGTZ.jpeg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KshDwaB.jpeg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4TMNEi3.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/cirenkoyenk\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴄɪʀᴇɴᴋ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_0d907aad-019b-4b72-8279-3a2fca522efc.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🕵 Detective","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":3308,"messages":49274,"created_at":"2024-07-22T15:51:52.058419+00:00"}